{"tid":1858572,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"家下3：00有無南區廢青廢中聽朝8：30上瑪麗撐銀髮族手足撐醫護","createTime":"2020-02-02T19:09:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-03T04:35:54.000Z","uid":179775,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8b4fa542b924e3ba9d789b72c1d850576d9d70fa","tid":1858572,"uid":179775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T19:09:18.000Z","msg":"【銀髮族與醫護同行】<br />\n<br />\n封關抗疫 救香港<br />\n不全面封關 不上班<br />\n<br />\n銀髮族早上將會在瑪麗醫院門外，派發白絲帶聲援醫護罷工行動， 向市民講解情況，林鄭理應盡快全面封關，停止源頭，武漢肺炎在社區爆發，情況急劇轉壞，陷前線醫護於水深火熱之中，極可能為了林鄭與高官嘅人禍而賠上性命！ <br />\n<br />\n醫管局員工陣線主席余慧明：「我相信面對天災，所有醫護都會做好天職，但係面對人禍，政府唔肯做嘢，置醫護生死於不顧，今次罷工係無可避免⋯是政府逼出來的。」<br />\n<br />\n日期：2月3日星期一<br />\n時間：上午8時半<br />\n地點：瑪麗醫院門外<br />\n<br />\n#與醫護同行<br />\n#不全面封關不上班<br />\n#全面封關刻不容緩"},{"pid":"9dbd7a7ebd49fd67a0727c6873967f6fe42bfcb5","tid":1858572,"uid":17838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T19:09:51.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c01088246f2c71118f785fbfda83c989b433ec26","tid":1858572,"uid":179775,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T19:12:36.000Z","msg":"早d瞓一陣上去幫手"},{"pid":"3b207f06bb758abdc4111aed7611dde86b502a88","tid":1858572,"uid":179775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T00:01:49.000Z","msg":"出發"},{"pid":"05e38a1abffab07a0f8f2dc20fd568d6cb066ace","tid":1858572,"uid":181549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T00:03:07.000Z","msg":"多謝你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b5331be41ac4b90dea02f2a63a8acc7acd9999c","tid":1858572,"uid":274608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T00:04:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d87817e42534119307fd649db28c9706d074686d","tid":1858572,